snippet.title: Alpaca Ball: Allstars - Announcement Trailer PC & SWITCH
snippet.description:
Wishlist Alpaca Ball: Allstars now on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/1232640/Alpaca_Ball_Allstars/ 

Football with Alpacas! Bring the cup home with up to 8 players in this hilarious and chaotic physics-based party game! Peru-ve yourself on the Picchu and win those Machus!

Keep up to date by following us on

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/saltcastlestudio/
